snippet.title: Become A Star - Trailer
snippet.description:
In Become a Star, play as a musician on his journey to success in this virtual reality rhythm game! Pick your instrument (guitar or drums), prepare your concerts on stage, and feel the crowd vibrate to the rhythm of original songs! The game will become available very soon in early access.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2295790/Become_A_Star/

Game features
- Play Drums Or Guitar
- Prepare For Live Performances
- See the Audience React to Your Performance
- Discover the band's Original Music
